Two,Tap,is,an,application,that,allows,mobile,and,web,application,publishers,and,developers,to,integrate,purchasing,and,buying,features,into,their,applications,Two,Tap,allows,app,users,to,purchase,things,directly,from,the,application,The,Two,Tap,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Two,Tap,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,adding,things,to,shopping,carts,sending,purchase,confirmation,and,retrieving,purchasing,information